# 🎉 Realtime Buffet Ordering System

A full-stack real-time web application for **buffet table booking and live food ordering**, built with **ReactJS, NodeJS, MySQL, Socket.io, TypeScript**, and more.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👨‍🍳 Client Side (User)
- Realtime buffet table reservation
- Live dish ordering system
- Secure authentication via **Access Token**
- Responsive UI with **Ant Design** & **Bootstrap**

### 🛠 Admin Side
- Role-based authorization (e.g., admin, staff)
- Protected routes via **JWT Access + Refresh Tokens**
- Manage tables, dishes, orders, users
- Realtime order tracking and notifications

### 🔧 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech                          |
|--------------|-------------------------------|
| Frontend     | ReactJS, TypeScript, Ant Design, Bootstrap |
| Backend      | NodeJS (Express), Socket.io   |
| Database     | MySQL                         |
| Auth         | JWT (Access & Refresh Tokens) |
| API Testing  | Postman                       |

---

## 🔐 Security & Authentication

- 🔑 **Access Token** (short-lived) for user & admin API access
- 🔄 **Refresh Token** (stored securely) for renewing access tokens (admin)
- 🛡️ **Role-based authorization** to control access to protected routes (e.g., `/admin`, `/staff`)
- Middleware checks and token validation on backend

---

## 🔄 Realtime Features (Socket.io)
- Live table booking updates
- Instant order updates to kitchen/admin dashboard
- Realtime notifications to clients & admins

